Definition.WordDefinition: Inexact \In`ex*act"\, a. [Pref. in- not + exact: cf. F. inexact.] Not exact; not precisely correct or true; inaccurate. [1913 Webster]
inexact adj 1: not exact [ant: {exact}] 2: not precisely accurate; "an inexact quotation" [syn: {inaccurate}]
